dataqual.logic:
Data are considered of good quality in the context of the information presented in the abstract.  Users are advised to read the rest of the metadata record carefully for additional details.&#xD;
Specific to carbon fluxes:&#xD;
QA/QC of CO2 fluxes closely followed that noted in Oberbauer et al. 2007&#xD;
QA/QC of CH4 fluxes closely followed that noted in Sachs et al. 2010 and Lund et al. 2009 &#xD;
